@rittneje just to make sure we're looking at the same thing, are you determining the schema by looking at the ManifestType field of the image.  For those two images I'm seeing:
```
temp1.0.0.txt:        "ManifestType": "application/vnd.docker.distribution.manifest.v2+json",
temp1.1.1.txt:        "ManifestType": "application/vnd.docker.distribution.manifest.v1+prettyjws",
```
@nalind any thoughts why the manifest type might have reverted?  My only thought is perhaps my test vm had an older version of podman when I built the images?
